posting_body: Gorgeous fully furnished DR Horton home for lease
Excellent location within walking distance to McKinney Falls State Park, minutes from downtown Austin, close to major employers, and near plenty of shopping choices
Fabulous finishes include sleek tile floors, recessed lighting, large closets, quartz bathroom countertops, high ceilings, covered patio, and more
Enjoy the gourmet kitchen offering granite countertops, gas range, and side by side stainless steel refrigerator
The bedrooms are spacious and bright containing high-end hotel quality beds, with a split floorplan giving the owner ultimate privacy
There are 3 queen beds and one king bed, providing enough room for guests or roommates alike
The primary bedroom as well as one of the spare bedrooms offers a desk for those who work from home
Space for an office or home gym available
The large backyard is perfect for entertaining and BBQing with friends
The community is close to golf courses, hiking trails, parks, and more - plenty of options to do and enjoy!
